ti a, a letlingin an khengbet ta a ni. A Lalpan,”Hengte ai hian kei
min hmangaih em?” a tih lai a ‘Lalpa ka hmangaih che,’ a ti theilo
kha a in haw ber a. Tunah chuan ,”Lalpa ka hmangaih che,” a
